As #Russia tries to control information about its war in #Ukraine, several other countries have recently restricted press freedom in similar ways.

@Rozen_J reports in @dailymaverick on common challenges faced by journalists covering conflict. 

#WPFD2022 https://t.co/vuGUPBqRRF

At least 3 journalists are spending #WorldPressFreedomDay behind bars in #Somaliland. They were part of a recent wave of arrests in the breakaway region.

@pressfreedom continues to call for their release.

https://t.co/AeRMriqjRD

#Ethiopia: Journalists Dessu Dulla and Bikila Amenu were detained in late 2021.

They remain behind bars and are due to appear in court today, #WorldPressFreedomDay. 

